WEBVTT

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:03.750
Well, good evening, everybody. Thank you

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:06.550
for joining us again tonight. We'll

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:08.070
go over some of the things the Lord

00:00:08.080 --> 00:00:10.870
showed us last Friday before I took

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:13.669
my break. We're backing up for

00:00:13.679 --> 00:00:16.310
another week of prayer. Thank you

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:18.310
for joining me, and we'll see what the

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:21.510
Lord has for us tonight. All glory

00:00:21.520 --> 00:00:25.109
to Jesus. Isn't Jesus wonderful?

00:00:25.119 --> 00:00:27.429
There's a lot happening in the news,

00:00:27.439 --> 00:00:30.390
isn't there?

00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:32.549
But tonight's video is 'The Valley of

00:00:32.549 --> 00:00:32.559
Decision'for

00:00:32.559 --> 00:00:35.510
what I'm praying over

00:00:35.520 --> 00:00:37.990
for President Trump

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:40.950
concerning his major decisions that

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:44.150
he's going to make. The Lord gave me

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:45.590
this in prayer, and I'm just going to

00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:47.430
jump right into it. I just felt the

00:00:47.430 --> 00:00:47.440
unction

00:00:47.440 --> 00:00:48.869
of the Holy Ghost. Thank you,

00:00:48.879 --> 00:00:53.189
Holy Spirit.

00:00:53.199 --> 00:00:56.310
When I was in prayer yesterday,

00:00:56.320 --> 00:00:57.750
I got caught up in the Spirit. Over

00:00:57.760 --> 00:01:00.630
the next two weeks—I want you to hear

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:02.630
this very

00:01:02.630 --> 00:01:02.640
carefully—major

00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:05.509
decisions will be made

00:01:05.519 --> 00:01:11.190
concerning Iran

00:01:11.190 --> 00:01:11.200
and

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:14.149
Pakistan.

00:01:14.159 --> 00:01:15.750
Major

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:18.070
disruptions are about to erupt in

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:19.830
Pakistan.

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:22.870
I saw Pakistan very clearly. The Lord

00:01:22.880 --> 00:01:24.630
said there are things about to take place.

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:26.230
Now, you might say, 'Well, Brandon, when

00:01:26.240 --> 00:01:27.350
is that going to take place?'I don't

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:29.670
know; I see in part,

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:32.230
but I saw Pakistan

00:01:32.230 --> 00:01:32.240
and

00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:36.789
Iran highlighted. As I saw

00:01:36.799 --> 00:01:39.910
this major thing about to happen in

00:01:39.920 --> 00:01:44.469
Iran, I heard anti-Semitism

00:01:44.479 --> 00:01:47.830
will be at an all-time high in the days

00:01:47.840 --> 00:01:49.670
ahead.

00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:54.230
I saw New York City again. I saw the

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:57.910
Jewish community in New York City and

00:01:57.920 --> 00:02:00.230
in other parts of the United States, as

00:02:00.230 --> 00:02:00.240
well as

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:02.469
Jewish communities

00:02:02.479 --> 00:02:05.990
in other nations,

00:02:05.990 --> 00:02:06.000
under

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:09.749
great persecution.

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:12.630
I saw great anti-Semitism coming at

00:02:12.640 --> 00:02:15.589
an all-time high in the days ahead

00:02:15.599 --> 00:02:19.270
concerning the Jewish people.

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:21.750
I saw great

00:02:21.750 --> 00:02:21.760
protests,

00:02:21.760 --> 00:02:23.830
and I saw that some of them were in

00:02:23.840 --> 00:02:25.350
danger.

00:02:25.360 --> 00:02:28.309
When I was shown this, I saw people

00:02:28.319 --> 00:02:31.190
fleeing to Israel.

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:33.190
They were uprooting their families in

00:02:33.200 --> 00:02:35.430
these major

00:02:35.440 --> 00:02:37.190
cities and they said, 'We've had

00:02:37.200 --> 00:02:39.430
enough.'They

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:41.350
were getting their things and

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:44.949
moving to Israel.

00:02:44.959 --> 00:02:48.150
I thought that was interesting. I

00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:49.990
told Diana, 'Would you look that

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:51.830
up, if what we're

00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:55.110
looking at is biblical?'She found scriptures

00:02:55.120 --> 00:02:57.350
about how God would bring the people back together after they

00:02:57.350 --> 00:02:57.360
were

00:02:57.360 --> 00:02:59.030
scattered

00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:04.070
in the end times. Like

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:05.830
I said, I'm not a Bible scholar when it

00:03:05.840 --> 00:03:07.509
comes to stuff like this. When I'm

00:03:07.519 --> 00:03:08.869
looking in the spirit and the Lord

00:03:08.869 --> 00:03:08.879
is

00:03:08.879 --> 00:03:11.509
showing me things, I thought it was

00:03:11.519 --> 00:03:13.509
interesting. He said He was

00:03:13.519 --> 00:03:16.070
bringing His people home. He was

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:18.790
bringing the Jewish people home. I

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:22.710
saw the Jews going to Israel in mass

00:03:22.720 --> 00:03:25.830
numbers from persecution that will arise

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:28.790
in the days ahead. They

00:03:28.800 --> 00:03:31.589
were all starting to come back to

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:35.110
Jerusalem.

00:03:35.120 --> 00:03:36.949
I thought that was interesting on a

00:03:36.959 --> 00:03:40.710
greater scale in the days ahead.

00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:47.589
I

00:03:47.599 --> 00:03:55.110
saw fires all over with great

00:03:55.110 --> 00:03:55.120
protests

00:03:55.120 --> 00:03:59.990
in New York City. I saw the

00:03:59.990 --> 00:04:00.000
forty-first

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:03.429
floor of a major building in New York

00:04:03.439 --> 00:04:06.869
City on fire again.

00:04:06.879 --> 00:04:11.190
I saw a lot of fires in

00:04:11.200 --> 00:04:13.750
buildings and rioting coming to New York

00:04:13.760 --> 00:04:15.750
in the days ahead. I thought that

00:04:15.760 --> 00:04:17.509
was interesting because He keeps

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:20.069
showing me this over and over

00:04:20.079 --> 00:04:24.310
again concerning New York.

00:04:24.320 --> 00:04:26.870
He was upset again

00:04:26.880 --> 00:04:28.790
when I was praying in the spirit about

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:32.150
the new mayor of New York and the

00:04:32.160 --> 00:04:36.950
decisions that are already being made.

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:41.830
So we saw that. Now, I

00:04:41.840 --> 00:04:43.670
will go over what the Lord showed us

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:45.510
Friday.

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:50.390
I saw young men being paid

00:04:50.400 --> 00:04:54.629
off by the drug cartel in Venezuela

00:04:54.639 --> 00:04:57.510
trying to raise up an army against our

00:04:57.520 --> 00:05:00.629
troops that have been on the

00:05:00.639 --> 00:05:04.469
ground in Venezuela, but it was toward

00:05:04.479 --> 00:05:11.189
Brazil. I saw Cuba devising a plan

00:05:11.189 --> 00:05:11.199
on

00:05:11.199 --> 00:05:15.029
how to create

00:05:15.039 --> 00:05:17.430
civil unrest

00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:22.550
in Venezuela

00:05:25.110 --> 00:05:25.120
and

00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:27.749
Colombia.

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:33.189
I saw the cartel. I saw great

00:05:33.199 --> 00:05:36.230
operations of cocaine

00:05:36.240 --> 00:05:40.550
distribution

00:05:40.550 --> 00:05:40.560
plants—huge

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:44.070
operations full of people who

00:05:44.070 --> 00:05:44.080
looked

00:05:44.080 --> 00:05:48.870
strung out

00:05:48.870 --> 00:05:48.880
and

00:05:48.880 --> 00:05:51.830
broken.

00:05:51.840 --> 00:05:55.430
I saw ten buildings that looked like

00:05:55.440 --> 00:05:57.430
metal buildings with waves, like wavy tin that you put on a chicken coop, a pig pen, or a barn. It was

00:06:07.759 --> 00:06:11.029
designed with metal on the

00:06:11.039 --> 00:06:12.390
outside, like stucco, but it was

00:06:12.400 --> 00:06:13.990
rusty.

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:15.510
It looked like it was rusty and

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:17.830
falling apart. There were white stains

00:06:17.840 --> 00:06:19.510
on the buildings. There was

00:06:19.520 --> 00:06:21.189
rust, and I could see where the nail

00:06:21.199 --> 00:06:23.110
holes were

00:06:23.110 --> 00:06:23.120
with

00:06:23.120 --> 00:06:25.189
rust coming down the sides of the

00:06:25.199 --> 00:06:26.790
buildings. I could see the roof, but they

00:06:26.790 --> 00:06:26.800
were

00:06:26.800 --> 00:06:29.749
manufacturing cocaine and drugs in them.

00:06:31.759 --> 00:06:34.070
It was all in Colombia on the border,

00:06:34.080 --> 00:06:36.710
and I saw major

00:06:36.720 --> 00:06:39.350
trafficking of drugs in those areas.

00:06:39.360 --> 00:06:42.309
As I was looking into this, I

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:45.670
saw highways

00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:49.909
that looked like veins

00:06:59.520 --> 00:07:03.510
spread out all over

00:07:05.199 --> 00:07:07.589
Europe,

00:07:07.599 --> 00:07:09.189
Africa,

00:07:09.199 --> 00:07:11.749
America, and Asia. I saw the

00:07:11.759 --> 00:07:14.710
Panama Canal, and they were taking the

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:16.550
drugs and distributing them

00:07:16.560 --> 00:07:20.870
into Asia.

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:25.110
I saw Cuba at high alert

00:07:25.110 --> 00:07:25.120
under

00:07:25.120 --> 00:07:30.309
great pressure.

00:07:30.319 --> 00:07:34.150
I saw their president

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:37.270
inside of a mountain.

00:07:37.280 --> 00:07:40.309
He was in a bunker in the mountain,

00:07:40.319 --> 00:07:44.550
hiding out, afraid of

00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:46.550
the United States coming in

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:49.029
and invading again like they did with

00:07:49.039 --> 00:07:51.670
Venezuela.

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:53.510
He was lying low. He was in the

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:55.589
ground

00:07:55.599 --> 00:07:57.909
similar to Saddam. He

00:07:57.919 --> 00:08:00.070
was hiding in that bunker,

00:08:00.080 --> 00:08:02.070
but this man was hiding.

00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:03.830
He's trying to be cocky because he

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:05.270
thinks he's protected by the

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:06.790
mountain. It would take something

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:08.950
like a bunker buster to get him because

00:08:08.960 --> 00:08:11.189
there was only one way in and one way

00:08:11.199 --> 00:08:13.909
out. I could see these men with

00:08:13.919 --> 00:08:15.749
berets on their heads—some were

00:08:17.270 --> 00:08:17.280
African-American—standing

00:08:19.440 --> 00:08:21.510
at the entrance of this vault. It

00:08:21.520 --> 00:08:24.869
looked like a massive metal structure

00:08:24.879 --> 00:08:26.710
with a huge door, like

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:28.390
something out of

00:08:28.400 --> 00:08:31.350
Doomsday Preppers.

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:32.870
I could see him

00:08:32.880 --> 00:08:35.509
again devising a plan to raise up

00:08:35.519 --> 00:08:39.829
soldiers to try to create havoc in

00:08:39.839 --> 00:08:42.389
Venezuela in the days ahead.

00:08:42.399 --> 00:08:45.269
How do we bring

00:08:45.279 --> 00:08:48.070
civil unrest and how do we destroy the

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:51.030
oil wells they're after?

00:08:51.040 --> 00:08:54.710
I saw huge

00:08:54.720 --> 00:08:57.110
white containers

00:08:57.120 --> 00:08:59.509
made to hold

00:09:08.399 --> 00:09:11.030
oil, and

00:09:11.040 --> 00:09:12.630
they were targeting them. Some were on the water and some were inland, but I could

00:09:12.640 --> 00:09:15.829
see these containers full of oil and they were targeting them. I saw drones flying in the sky. I could

00:09:15.839 --> 00:09:18.630
see our

00:09:18.640 --> 00:09:21.509
Marines protecting these places

00:09:21.519 --> 00:09:24.389
with heavy artillery,

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:27.670
ready in case.

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:29.829
The Lord kept saying,

00:09:29.829 --> 00:09:29.839
'Guerrilla

00:09:29.839 --> 00:09:31.990
warfare, guerrilla

00:09:31.990 --> 00:09:32.000
warfare.'I

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:34.230
could hear

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:36.389
people coming out of the jungles

00:09:36.399 --> 00:09:39.190
threatening these young men

00:09:39.190 --> 00:09:39.200
in

00:09:39.200 --> 00:09:41.430
the cartel: 'If you don't do what we tell

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:43.190
you, we'll eliminate your whole

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:45.269
family.

00:09:45.279 --> 00:09:47.990
You fight for us or we will take out

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:50.550
your grandma, your mama,

00:09:50.550 --> 00:09:50.560
and

00:09:50.560 --> 00:09:52.389
all your sisters and

00:09:52.389 --> 00:09:52.399
force

00:09:52.399 --> 00:09:53.829
them into

00:09:54.870 --> 00:09:54.880
slavery.'I

00:09:58.080 --> 00:09:59.990
saw these young men in white

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:02.949
T-shirts. They didn't look like they

00:10:02.959 --> 00:10:06.070
had much. Some had longer hair,

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:07.750
but

00:10:07.750 --> 00:10:07.760
they

00:10:07.760 --> 00:10:09.430
looked like they were being forced

00:10:09.440 --> 00:10:11.190
to fight.

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:14.069
I saw them being given guns

00:10:14.069 --> 00:10:14.079
and

00:10:14.079 --> 00:10:17.030
going into jungle

00:10:17.040 --> 00:10:19.670
warfare. Some of these people, especially from Cuba, were very

00:10:19.680 --> 00:10:23.269
familiar with the terrain.

00:10:25.440 --> 00:10:27.990
I saw over ten

00:10:27.990 --> 00:10:28.000
thousand

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:30.389
people

00:10:30.399 --> 00:10:32.230
trying to infiltrate to take the land

00:10:32.230 --> 00:10:32.240
and

00:10:32.240 --> 00:10:34.550
cause havoc for America in

00:10:34.560 --> 00:10:37.430
the days ahead. This was also concerning

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:40.790
Colombia.

00:10:40.800 --> 00:10:43.829
I saw things coming for Colombia. I saw

00:10:43.839 --> 00:10:46.710
Claudia

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:50.870
pacing back and forth in a room

00:10:50.870 --> 00:10:50.880
with

00:10:50.880 --> 00:10:54.630
old antique furniture. It was

00:10:54.640 --> 00:10:57.750
beautiful cherrywood furniture. It

00:10:57.760 --> 00:11:00.389
looked like something out of

00:11:00.389 --> 00:11:00.399
the

00:11:00.399 --> 00:11:02.069
Victorian

00:11:02.069 --> 00:11:02.079
era.

00:11:02.079 --> 00:11:04.069
It looked very Victorian where she was.

00:11:04.079 --> 00:11:07.509
She was in a room and on the

00:11:07.519 --> 00:11:13.190
phone talking to the Colombian

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:14.949
president? I don't

00:11:14.959 --> 00:11:16.870
know who he was or what his

00:11:16.870 --> 00:11:16.880
title

00:11:16.880 --> 00:11:18.870
is,

00:11:18.870 --> 00:11:18.880
but

00:11:18.880 --> 00:11:20.790
she was talking to him. He acted cocky

00:11:20.800 --> 00:11:23.190
like he didn't care. She was pacing back

00:11:23.200 --> 00:11:26.470
and forth with nervous energy.

00:11:26.480 --> 00:11:29.430
I could see her in her room pacing back

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:31.990
and forth, asking, 'What do we do?'She's afraid

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:34.389
for her life because of the cartel that

00:11:34.399 --> 00:11:37.910
is backing her. At

00:11:37.920 --> 00:11:40.230
times she acted like she was scared

00:11:40.240 --> 00:11:42.870
for everything because of what's

00:11:42.880 --> 00:11:45.509
coming: a storm.

00:11:45.519 --> 00:11:47.590
I told you a major revival is about to

00:11:47.600 --> 00:11:51.190
hit Mexico. I saw liberation coming

00:11:51.200 --> 00:11:53.910
for the

00:11:53.920 --> 00:11:57.110
Mexican people, and for Colombia,

00:11:57.120 --> 00:12:02.710
Venezuela, and Cuba. A major

00:12:02.720 --> 00:12:06.470
revival is coming to South America. It's

00:12:06.480 --> 00:12:08.150
already, I believe, taking place in

00:12:08.160 --> 00:12:10.389
Brazil, but the Lord showed me a major

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:12.310
revival coming in the days ahead for

00:12:15.600 --> 00:12:18.550
all of South America. But

00:12:18.560 --> 00:12:20.790
as I was seeing the head of state be

00:12:20.800 --> 00:12:22.870
cut,

00:12:22.880 --> 00:12:26.069
the drug distribution and oil revenue,

00:12:26.079 --> 00:12:28.629
this was about major business concerning

00:12:28.639 --> 00:12:31.190
backing the dollar and all the things

00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:34.550
coming for the dollar, trying to sustain

00:12:34.560 --> 00:12:37.110
life in America. This is what I thought

00:12:37.120 --> 00:12:39.509
was interesting. Remember I told you I

00:12:39.519 --> 00:12:41.990
saw the prime minister of

00:12:42.000 --> 00:12:43.110
Italy—the

00:12:43.120 --> 00:12:47.030
woman? She does not

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:50.069
like the situation with Greenland, and the Lord

00:12:50.079 --> 00:12:51.910
warned us how many times about her

00:12:51.920 --> 00:12:56.310
standing up with Mark in Canada,

00:12:56.320 --> 00:12:59.590
England,

00:13:02.710 --> 00:13:02.720
Macron,

00:13:04.720 --> 00:13:08.710
Germany, Finland, and these nations.

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:12.310
And I saw a major business deal coming

00:13:12.320 --> 00:13:15.269
about with the United States of America

00:13:15.279 --> 00:13:18.550
offering each person in Greenland a sum

00:13:18.560 --> 00:13:21.269
of money. It was over $20,000 per

00:13:21.279 --> 00:13:24.230
citizen.

00:13:24.240 --> 00:13:27.829
It was divided fifty-fifty. I saw a vote

00:13:27.839 --> 00:13:29.750
coming,

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:32.389
but it was split fifty-fifty. A lot of the

00:13:32.399 --> 00:13:35.030
young people were excited about it; the

00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:38.550
elders weren't. I saw

00:13:38.560 --> 00:13:39.829
something with the fishing

00:13:39.839 --> 00:13:42.069
industry.

00:13:42.079 --> 00:13:44.870
The elders wanted to keep

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:46.710
the way they've always lived,

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:48.389
but it was about

00:13:48.399 --> 00:13:50.069
minerals and all these things.

00:13:50.079 --> 00:13:52.710
And I saw Trump say, 'I'm going to

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:56.949
strongarm

00:13:56.959 --> 00:13:59.269
them.'This

00:13:59.279 --> 00:14:00.710
is where the vision

00:14:00.720 --> 00:14:03.750
stopped. I didn't see that they became a

00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:06.230
part of America,

00:14:06.240 --> 00:14:07.670
so I don't want to add to or take away

00:14:07.680 --> 00:14:09.829
from anything.

00:14:11.920 --> 00:14:15.350
But as I saw a shaking coming

00:14:15.360 --> 00:14:18.629
to Canada—specifically British

00:14:18.629 --> 00:14:18.639
Columbia—I

00:14:18.639 --> 00:14:22.230
saw they would

00:14:22.240 --> 00:14:25.750
secede from Canada in the days ahead and

00:14:25.760 --> 00:14:28.870
become a part of America.

00:14:28.880 --> 00:14:31.509
British Columbia would try to pull

00:14:31.519 --> 00:14:33.910
away from Canada because of financial

00:14:33.920 --> 00:14:37.509
trouble that's coming.

00:14:37.519 --> 00:14:41.110
I told you I saw Taiwan,

00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:44.790
and I keep seeing Taiwan.

00:14:44.800 --> 00:14:47.750
I saw an escalation of things

00:14:47.750 --> 00:14:47.760
where

00:14:47.760 --> 00:14:51.189
China was trying to devise a plan with

00:14:51.199 --> 00:14:54.550
their generals for taking Taiwan.

00:14:54.560 --> 00:14:58.230
When I see this dome of prayer, I

00:14:58.240 --> 00:15:02.870
heard the Lord say, 'You can delay

00:15:02.880 --> 00:15:07.189
the

00:15:07.189 --> 00:15:07.199
inevitable.'You

00:15:07.199 --> 00:15:09.590
can delay this

00:15:09.600 --> 00:15:13.750
through prayer. I saw a golden dome

00:15:13.760 --> 00:15:16.470
come up over Taiwan

00:15:16.480 --> 00:15:19.030
on all sides

00:15:19.040 --> 00:15:21.110
through prayer. But as I was

00:15:21.120 --> 00:15:23.670
interceding, the Lord said they have not

00:15:23.680 --> 00:15:25.670
taken their freedom

00:15:25.680 --> 00:15:30.310
from the communist regime of China

00:15:30.320 --> 00:15:32.790
seriously over the years. They've taken

00:15:32.800 --> 00:15:35.829
their freedoms for granted and

00:15:35.829 --> 00:15:35.839
haven't prayed

00:15:35.839 --> 00:15:39.350
enough. As I

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:41.509
was looking into South Korea, the

00:15:41.519 --> 00:15:43.509
Lord said it will even be challenging

00:15:43.519 --> 00:15:46.550
in the days concerning South Korea, and a

00:15:46.560 --> 00:15:50.629
communist dragon will try to grab

00:15:50.629 --> 00:15:50.639
onto

00:15:50.639 --> 00:15:53.749
South Korea. But because there's more

00:15:53.759 --> 00:15:57.110
prayer root there,

00:15:57.120 --> 00:15:59.749
it will be held back.

00:15:59.759 --> 00:16:03.749
As long as my people in South Korea

00:16:03.759 --> 00:16:06.230
intercede and pray,

00:16:06.240 --> 00:16:08.790
it will hold back communism

00:16:08.790 --> 00:16:08.800
from

00:16:08.800 --> 00:16:10.550
their nation.

00:16:10.560 --> 00:16:12.949
As long as they humble themselves and

00:16:12.959 --> 00:16:15.990
pray, turning from their

00:16:16.000 --> 00:16:17.829
wicked ways, He

00:16:17.839 --> 00:16:21.110
said, 'Brandon, I will have a hedge of

00:16:21.120 --> 00:16:25.910
my protection over South

00:16:25.910 --> 00:16:25.920
Korea.'I

00:16:25.920 --> 00:16:28.389
saw it trying to infiltrate. It was a Chinese-looking

00:16:28.389 --> 00:16:28.399
spirit,

00:16:28.399 --> 00:16:30.150
like a snake

00:16:30.150 --> 00:16:30.160
or

00:16:30.160 --> 00:16:33.030
a dragon coming out of China into North

00:16:33.040 --> 00:16:35.829
Korea, trying to come over.

00:16:37.759 --> 00:16:40.310
It

00:16:40.320 --> 00:16:42.389
was a bad way of thinking through their

00:16:42.399 --> 00:16:44.949
government and their politics.

00:16:44.959 --> 00:16:47.829
He said it's trying to get a

00:16:47.839 --> 00:16:50.629
stronghold through

00:16:50.639 --> 00:16:52.710
their leaders.

00:16:52.720 --> 00:16:55.430
They don't have the right leaders. Pray

00:16:55.440 --> 00:16:58.870
for their leaders;

00:16:58.880 --> 00:17:02.069
it's an infiltration from China coming

00:17:02.079 --> 00:17:05.189
in through North Korea. It's a spirit

00:17:05.199 --> 00:17:09.110
that's trying to hook them,

00:17:09.120 --> 00:17:11.510
but they will be a major pillar in the

00:17:11.510 --> 00:17:11.520
end-time

00:17:11.520 --> 00:17:17.590
church.

00:17:17.600 --> 00:17:20.470
Revival will go out from there

00:17:20.480 --> 00:17:23.270
if they pray.

00:17:23.280 --> 00:17:26.230
But I saw Taiwan with this

00:17:26.240 --> 00:17:28.630
golden dome

00:17:28.640 --> 00:17:32.070
on all sides; if the people will pray. If

00:17:32.080 --> 00:17:34.549
they don't, they'll fall within three

00:17:34.559 --> 00:17:36.070
days.

00:17:36.080 --> 00:17:38.870
I saw they'll fight for one day,

00:17:38.870 --> 00:17:38.880
then

00:17:38.880 --> 00:17:41.110
into the second, but by the end

00:17:41.120 --> 00:17:43.270
of the second day, it will completely

00:17:43.280 --> 00:17:46.549
fold. I saw the Chinese government using

00:17:46.559 --> 00:17:48.630
weapons that have never been used

00:17:48.640 --> 00:17:51.110
before, similar to what America did to

00:17:51.120 --> 00:17:54.630
Venezuela. They have the same technological

00:17:54.630 --> 00:17:54.640
weaponry

00:17:54.640 --> 00:18:00.789
capabilities,

00:18:00.799 --> 00:18:03.669
maybe even better in some ways. I

00:18:03.669 --> 00:18:03.679
still

00:18:03.679 --> 00:18:07.350
believe America

00:18:07.350 --> 00:18:07.360
is

00:18:07.360 --> 00:18:09.750
top,

00:18:09.760 --> 00:18:11.590
but there were things that China had that

00:18:11.600 --> 00:18:14.549
even America didn't

00:18:14.549 --> 00:18:14.559
have—secret

00:18:14.559 --> 00:18:16.549
things—and

00:18:16.559 --> 00:18:20.150
they would use them as a flex.

00:18:20.160 --> 00:18:23.029
These people had artillery,

00:18:23.039 --> 00:18:25.190
but it was no match

00:18:25.190 --> 00:18:25.200
for

00:18:25.200 --> 00:18:27.350
what China would try to do. It fell

00:18:27.360 --> 00:18:31.510
in three days,

00:18:31.510 --> 00:18:31.520
just

00:18:31.520 --> 00:18:37.750
like

00:18:37.750 --> 00:18:37.760
that.

00:18:37.760 --> 00:18:39.510
When I see all

00:18:39.520 --> 00:18:40.870
these things in the spirit and the Lord

00:18:40.880 --> 00:18:43.430
warns me,

00:18:43.440 --> 00:18:45.110
I know we can pray. That's why the

00:18:45.120 --> 00:18:46.950
Lord said, 'Cover them in prayer.'I saw a

00:18:46.960 --> 00:18:49.590
dome of glory around them, and He said,

00:18:49.600 --> 00:18:51.830
'You can hold it and delay the

00:18:51.840 --> 00:18:53.590
inevitable of what will come in the days

00:18:53.590 --> 00:18:53.600
ahead.'Delay

00:18:53.600 --> 00:18:57.750
it. But as I saw Trump say

00:18:57.760 --> 00:19:05.830
this right here—you can play it:

00:19:05.840 --> 00:19:06.710
'It

00:19:06.720 --> 00:19:13.590
is

00:19:13.600 --> 00:19:17.110
a source of pride for him. He considers it to

00:19:17.120 --> 00:19:21.110
be a part of China, and that's up to

00:19:21.120 --> 00:19:23.350
him what he's going to be doing. But

00:19:23.360 --> 00:19:25.510
I've expressed to him that I would

00:19:25.520 --> 00:19:28.710
be very unhappy if he did that, and I

00:19:28.720 --> 00:19:30.470
don't think he'll do that. I hope he

00:19:30.480 --> 00:19:30.950
doesn't do that.

00:19:30.960 --> 00:19:31.909
So you don't think you've set a

00:19:31.909 --> 00:19:31.919
precedent?

00:19:31.919 --> 00:19:34.950
He may do it after we have a

00:19:34.960 --> 00:19:36.950
different president, but I don't think

00:19:36.960 --> 00:19:38.310
he's going to do it with me as

00:19:38.320 --> 00:19:39.110
president.

00:19:39.120 --> 00:19:40.950
Supposing you're Xi Jinping and

00:19:40.960 --> 00:19:44.230
you've watched the events of the past;

00:19:44.230 --> 00:19:44.240
you're

00:19:44.240 --> 00:19:48.150
probably impressed with

00:19:51.190 --> 00:19:51.200
it.''The

00:19:53.440 --> 00:19:54.950
special

00:19:54.950 --> 00:19:54.960
operators—he

00:19:54.960 --> 00:19:57.029
was impressed. You may also be

00:19:57.039 --> 00:19:59.190
thinking that if you're Xi, you

00:19:59.200 --> 00:20:01.350
could use the same logic to decapitate

00:20:01.360 --> 00:20:04.710
and control Taiwan, or why couldn't Putin

00:20:04.720 --> 00:20:06.789
use that same argument

00:20:06.799 --> 00:20:09.430
to grab the rest of Ukraine or go

00:20:09.440 --> 00:20:11.669
beyond into other former Soviet states?

00:20:11.679 --> 00:20:13.430
In other words, have you created a

00:20:13.440 --> 00:20:15.590
precedent that you may come to regret

00:20:15.600 --> 00:20:16.230
later

00:20:16.230 --> 00:20:16.240
on?''No.

00:20:16.240 --> 00:20:18.070
Because this was a real

00:20:18.080 --> 00:20:20.549
threat. You didn't have people pouring

00:20:20.559 --> 00:20:23.909
into China. You didn't have drugs

00:20:23.919 --> 00:20:25.669
pouring into China.

00:20:25.679 --> 00:20:27.110
You didn't have

00:20:27.120 --> 00:20:29.190
the

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:32.470
jails of Taiwan opened up and the people

00:20:32.480 --> 00:20:34.070
pouring into China. There aren't that

00:20:34.080 --> 00:20:36.390
many people in the jails, but you

00:20:36.400 --> 00:20:38.310
didn't have hundreds of thousands of

00:20:38.320 --> 00:20:41.190
people coming from jails and mental

00:20:41.200 --> 00:20:42.390
institutions.

00:20:42.400 --> 00:20:46.390
But

00:20:46.390 --> 00:20:46.400
Taiwan—she

00:20:46.400 --> 00:20:48.870
would tell you Taiwan's a threat to

00:20:48.880 --> 00:20:52.630
China, that it's a separatist operation.

00:20:53.120 --> 00:20:54.390
What's the source of

00:20:54.400 --> 00:20:55.029
Xi's

00:20:55.039 --> 00:20:56.149
pride for

00:20:56.149 --> 00:20:56.159
him?'So

00:20:56.159 --> 00:20:58.870
in his mind, it's already

00:20:58.880 --> 00:21:00.630
theirs.

00:21:00.640 --> 00:21:03.750
The way it sounded to me,

00:21:03.760 --> 00:21:05.510
if they take it, I hope he doesn't do

00:21:05.520 --> 00:21:07.350
it in my term, but even then, it didn't

00:21:07.360 --> 00:21:09.909
sound like he's going to resist it. So

00:21:09.919 --> 00:21:11.909
maybe he will, maybe he won't, I don't

00:21:11.919 --> 00:21:13.510
know. So it kind of went with what I've

00:21:13.520 --> 00:21:16.549
been seeing. Number two was praying

00:21:16.559 --> 00:21:19.350
over what I saw about the

00:21:19.360 --> 00:21:22.470
government coming in, and I saw Russia

00:21:22.480 --> 00:21:25.270
come in and just take out Zelensky

00:21:25.270 --> 00:21:25.280
and

00:21:25.280 --> 00:21:27.510
their government and all

00:21:27.520 --> 00:21:29.510
the things that are escalating in

00:21:29.520 --> 00:21:31.350
Europe.

00:21:31.360 --> 00:21:33.430
So you've seen a lot of the shorts that

00:21:33.440 --> 00:21:35.350
my son has been making. He has been hard

00:21:35.360 --> 00:21:38.070
at work, hasn't he? Making shorts and

00:21:38.080 --> 00:21:40.390
making drawings. You know, everybody

00:21:40.400 --> 00:21:41.990
said, 'Brandon, can you comment on some

00:21:42.000 --> 00:21:43.909
of these things that you posted?'No,

00:21:43.909 --> 00:21:43.919
it's—we

00:21:43.919 --> 00:21:46.870
did it like The Economist.

00:21:46.880 --> 00:21:49.510
We were having fun putting on there.

00:21:49.520 --> 00:21:51.990
There's no explanation. I'm not here to

00:21:52.000 --> 00:21:54.310
interpret a

00:21:54.320 --> 00:21:57.029
vision of what I've seen. I put

00:21:57.039 --> 00:22:00.070
on what I saw.

00:22:00.080 --> 00:22:02.710
Now, The Economist doesn't interpret

00:22:02.720 --> 00:22:05.830
what they put on there and tell you, 'This

00:22:05.840 --> 00:22:08.390
is what we're trying to

00:22:08.390 --> 00:22:08.400
say.'You

00:22:08.400 --> 00:22:13.190
pray about it.

00:22:13.200 --> 00:22:15.909
You pray about every person that I

00:22:15.919 --> 00:22:18.390
put on there.

00:22:18.400 --> 00:22:20.310
I'm not saying the Lord didn't

00:22:20.320 --> 00:22:22.710
tell me to do that. He said, 'Be bold

00:22:22.720 --> 00:22:24.710
and put this on there and then walk

00:22:24.710 --> 00:22:24.720
away.'So

00:22:24.720 --> 00:22:27.590
that's what we did, and we're

00:22:27.600 --> 00:22:29.990
making a new one. It's going to be

00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:31.909
even better than this last one. Braden

00:22:31.919 --> 00:22:34.070
said, 'That was fun. I enjoyed that.

00:22:34.080 --> 00:22:35.909
Let's make another one.'So we're making

00:22:35.919 --> 00:22:37.590
another one. It will be even more

00:22:37.600 --> 00:22:39.510
detailed. The next one we work on is

00:22:39.520 --> 00:22:42.230
going to be a piece of work, but

00:22:42.240 --> 00:22:45.590
it's going to be an amazing art piece.

00:22:45.600 --> 00:22:47.590
I'm excited about it. I told him,

00:22:47.600 --> 00:22:49.190
'We'll work on this for a

00:22:49.200 --> 00:22:51.430
couple of days, a week or so, whatever,

00:22:51.440 --> 00:22:52.950
and then we'll present it to the people,

00:22:52.960 --> 00:22:54.630
and they can look at it.'But it's all

00:22:54.640 --> 00:22:57.190
the things the Lord has shown me in

00:22:57.200 --> 00:22:58.870
visions,

00:22:58.880 --> 00:23:00.630
and we put it together and just

00:23:00.640 --> 00:23:03.270
present it to the people.

00:23:03.280 --> 00:23:06.149
So, pretty neat, I guess.

00:23:06.159 --> 00:23:08.230
So, was that it?

00:23:08.240 --> 00:23:10.789
No.

00:23:11.200 --> 00:23:12.870
Play this.

00:23:12.880 --> 00:23:14.630
Now this is interesting. This is the

00:23:14.640 --> 00:23:16.390
head of the NATO army, I guess.

00:23:16.400 --> 00:23:18.950
Yes.

00:23:18.960 --> 00:23:21.029
Can you play what he says? This is

00:23:21.039 --> 00:23:26.390
pretty interesting.

00:23:26.390 --> 00:23:26.400
Experience

00:23:26.400 --> 00:23:29.990
of the two nations'militaries,

00:23:29.990 --> 00:23:30.000
a

00:23:30.000 --> 00:23:33.190
deep commitment to the alliance, and

00:23:33.200 --> 00:23:35.990
a sense of urgency—and that sense of

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:39.029
urgency is essential. When I look around

00:23:39.039 --> 00:23:43.990
the globe—Russia, China, Iran, North

00:23:44.000 --> 00:23:46.630
Korea, and others are increasing their

00:23:46.640 --> 00:23:49.669
collaboration and their cooperation as

00:23:49.679 --> 00:23:53.350
their interests align against us.

00:23:53.360 --> 00:23:56.710
We see this clearly in Ukraine.

00:23:56.720 --> 00:23:58.549
While President Trump pushes for a

00:23:58.559 --> 00:24:01.590
peaceful resolution to a horrible war,

00:24:01.600 --> 00:24:04.070
China continues to fund Putin's war

00:24:04.080 --> 00:24:05.590
machine.

00:24:05.600 --> 00:24:09.590
Iran continues to supply technology and

00:24:09.600 --> 00:24:11.110
weapons,

00:24:11.120 --> 00:24:14.070
and North Korean combat troops remain in

00:24:14.080 --> 00:24:17.269
Russia on Ukraine's border.

00:24:17.279 --> 00:24:19.350
And of course, there's a confluence

00:24:19.360 --> 00:24:22.630
between Russia, Iran, and Venezuela and

00:24:22.640 --> 00:24:25.110
their dark fleet of oil tankers that is

00:24:25.120 --> 00:24:27.750
helping to fund the war.

00:24:27.760 --> 00:24:29.590
In the Arctic and the High North, we see

00:24:29.600 --> 00:24:32.390
a similar trend. Russian and Chinese

00:24:32.400 --> 00:24:34.230
vessels are conducting more and more

00:24:34.240 --> 00:24:37.430
joint patrols. Chinese icebreakers and

00:24:37.440 --> 00:24:40.870
research vessels are in Arctic waters,

00:24:40.880 --> 00:24:43.190
and their research is not for peaceful

00:24:43.200 --> 00:24:44.789
purposes.

00:24:44.799 --> 00:24:48.310
It's to gain a military advantage.

00:24:48.320 --> 00:24:50.710
Russia, meanwhile, continues testing

00:24:50.720 --> 00:24:55.190
advanced capabilities in the Barents Sea.

00:24:55.200 --> 00:24:57.269
As new shipping routes emerge and new

00:24:57.279 --> 00:24:59.430
resources are discovered, the Arctic

00:24:59.440 --> 00:25:02.549
only grows in strategic importance. And

00:25:02.559 --> 00:25:04.950
all of this comes in the midst of an

00:25:04.960 --> 00:25:07.590
increasing hybrid threat: airspace

00:25:07.600 --> 00:25:09.110
violations,

00:25:09.120 --> 00:25:12.549
GPS and GNSS interference, and the

00:25:12.559 --> 00:25:14.470
shadow fleet in the Baltic Sea

00:25:14.480 --> 00:25:18.230
threatening underwater infrastructure.

00:25:18.240 --> 00:25:20.630
In short, the Arctic and Northern Europe

00:25:20.640 --> 00:25:23.510
by extension have become a frontline for

00:25:23.520 --> 00:25:26.549
strategic competition

00:25:26.559 --> 00:25:29.029
within NATO Allied Command Operations.

00:25:29.039 --> 00:25:31.510
The command that SACEUR oversees has

00:25:31.520 --> 00:25:33.350
taken steps to strengthen our deterrent

00:25:33.360 --> 00:25:36.390
posture, much of which is oriented in

00:25:36.400 --> 00:25:39.750
that northern region here.

00:25:39.760 --> 00:25:41.669
Just over a year ago, we established

00:25:41.679 --> 00:25:43.350
Baltic

00:25:43.350 --> 00:25:43.360
Sentinel,

00:25:43.360 --> 00:25:45.110
an activity.

00:25:45.120 --> 00:25:53.269
Yeah. And then Cuba,

00:25:53.279 --> 00:25:55.110
and then he had... what is

00:25:55.120 --> 00:25:57.830
it? Committee address. United States and

00:25:57.840 --> 00:26:00.149
Russia... and he posted something in

00:26:00.159 --> 00:26:01.830
Russian.

00:26:01.840 --> 00:26:03.669
Who

00:26:03.679 --> 00:26:06.230
did that? 'United States is miscalculating

00:26:06.240 --> 00:26:08.950
today in retaliation to Iran.'I don't

00:26:08.960 --> 00:26:11.269
know. He made a post

00:26:11.279 --> 00:26:13.029
in Russian.

00:26:13.029 --> 00:26:13.039
Why'd

00:26:13.039 --> 00:26:14.390
he put it in Russian?

00:26:14.400 --> 00:26:16.390
I don't know. I think maybe

00:26:16.400 --> 00:26:18.070
his normal account got banned.

00:26:18.080 --> 00:26:20.070
But he did have a Russian

00:26:20.080 --> 00:26:26.789
account.

00:26:26.799 --> 00:26:28.950
I wonder what that means.

00:26:28.960 --> 00:26:30.390
Yeah, because there's a reason he chose

00:26:30.400 --> 00:26:31.190
Russian.

00:26:31.919 --> 00:26:33.350
I wonder if there's a reason he chose

00:26:33.360 --> 00:26:33.830
Russian.

00:26:33.830 --> 00:26:33.840
I'm

00:26:33.840 --> 00:26:36.149
just telling you, that guy...

00:26:36.159 --> 00:26:39.430
I pray that his

00:26:39.440 --> 00:26:41.909
days are numbered.

00:26:41.919 --> 00:26:46.110
He's a very bad man.

00:26:47.440 --> 00:26:49.190
Interesting.

00:26:49.200 --> 00:26:51.350
Well, I guess that's it for that part of

00:26:51.360 --> 00:26:53.269
it. You know, we can pray now and

00:26:53.279 --> 00:26:56.070
we'll see what the Lord shows us.

00:26:56.080 --> 00:26:58.149
We bring all this stuff to you. Braden

